msgid "Requires categories of the form images from Wiki Loves <strong><em>project</em></strong> in a specific <strong><em>year</em></strong>, eg “Images from Wiki Loves <strong><em>Africa</em></strong> <strong><em>2019</em></strong>” (change <strong><em>project</em></strong> and year as <strong><em>required</em></strong>)"
msgstr "Vul hier categorieën in in het formaat images from Wiki Loves <strong><em>project</em></strong> in een specifiek <strong><em>jaar</em></strong>, bijvoorbeeld \"Images from Wiki Loves <strong><em>Africa</em></strong> <strong><em>2019</em></strong>” (pas <strong><em>project</em></strong> en jaar aan als <strong><em>dat nodig is</em></strong>)"

